	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Sat, Jan 5th 4:54 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=121232><span id= >Fluxus</span></a><br><span id=notbold>153 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Excellent post Slipskin!<br><br>Just to add a little more info..<br><br>I'm a halfling rogue on Tarew Marr (25th lvl).&nbsp;&nbsp;Once I hit 14th I went to Oasis of Marr.  The loot is terrible, but the experience is very good and groups aren't hard to find.  Try to partner with a druid there and team up on crocs.  They can snare and Fear Animal and you get to backstab 'em to death.<br><br>At about 18-20 go to South Karana and team up on either Aviaks or gnolls at the spires.  Here the loot is very good and the exp is excellent.  You can also pop back in to NK and solo the wisps.  Trade the greater lightstones in to one of the gypsy women for 8pp each.  I think her name is Myrsalla or something like that.<br><br>Once you get 200-300pp I'd go to EC and buy.  You can get some decent STR earrings for about 100 a pair.  Same with Rings.  I'm still wearing orc fang earrings and jagged band rings (+12 str all together).<br><br>For weapons, I use the crystal grinder in primary, jagged chokidai spine in secondary and dragoon dirk in range (don't throw it).  You can get any of these weapons for 100-300pp.<br><br>Rogues are the gods of dealing damage.  You have to constantly keep upgrading gear to improve STR and getting better weapons.  Because you deal out so much pain, you'll need to control aggro with evade.  Set up a hotkey to evade so you can duck out of combat momentarily and give the real tank a chance to get back up on the hate list.  Then, just fire off another BS.  :-)<br><br>Good luck with your halfling rogue.  IMO, they are the best.</p>&nbsp;<br>Fluxus<br>58 Rogue<br>Tarew Marr<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=138160" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=138160</a></td></tr>
